<item>
            <title>[LU-6440] Update ZFS/SPL version to 0.6.3-1.3</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6440</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;New point point release of SPL &amp;amp; ZFS has been released:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Changes:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Update code to use misc_register()/misc_deregister()&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Use current_kernel_time() in the time compatibility wrappers&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Linux 3.12 compat: split shrinker has s_shrink&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Linux 3.19 compat: file_inode was added&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Linux 4.0 compat: bdi_setup_and_register()&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
